4-02T09:57:02.422Z\"},\"title_zh\":\"GLM-5\",\"title_en\":\"GLM-5\",\"desc_zh\":\"GLM-5 达到开源模型 SOTA，比肩 Claude Opus 4.5\",\"desc_en\":\"GLM-5 achieves open-source SoTA—surpassing all previous open models and matching Claude Opus 4.5\",\"showNew\":false,\"active\":true,\"order\":3,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T03:58:06.837Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-19T12:46:38.424Z\"},{\"id\":5,\"article\":{\"id\":145,\"title_zh\":\"AutoGLM开源：每台手机，都可以成为AI手机\",\"title_en\":\"AutoGLM Goes Open Source\",\"createAt\":\"2025-12-08T16:00:00.000Z\",\"category\":\"blog\",\"resume_zh\":\"\",\"resume_en\":\"Unlocking the AI Phone for Everyone\",\"contentType_zh\":\"content\",\"externalUrl_zh\":null,\"content_zh\":{\"root\":{\"children\":[{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们想做的，到底是一件什么事\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"left\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"过去的很长时间，我们一直在回答同一个问题：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"如果 AI 真的是“助手”，它能不能像人一样，自己把手机拿起来，把一件事从头做到尾？\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在我们的想象里，AI 不该只停留在聊天框里，而是可以走进用户每天真正要点的那些 App 里：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"帮你在外卖 App 里完成从选择到下单；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"帮你在云手机里，批量处理通知、点赞评论；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"帮你在销售、客服、出勤等场景里，自动做完一堆“你自己也不想点的重复动作”。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"AutoGLM 想做的，就是这件事：让 AI 真正学会“使用手机”。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"32个月，我们具体做到了什么？\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"left\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"left\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"用一句简单的话来说：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们希望 AutoGLM，不仅能“说”，还能“做”。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"为了这一句话，我们从 2023 年 4 月——一个大多数人还不知道大模型是什么的时候，完全从零去探索每一个细节，到今天，已经 32 个月了。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"1.“乱点” -\u003e “可控”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h3\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在最开始的版本里，基于大模型所构建的系统只知道“点”、“滑”等操作，偶尔能完成一个很短的流程，更多时候会迷失在不知所谓的操作中，甚至陷入死循环。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"为了解决这类问题，我们花了近一年的时间，去梳理每一个可能的问题，尝试把这些“乱点的手”变成一只“\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"可控的手”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"建了一整套 Phone Use 能力框架；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"把点击、滑动、输入、截图、界面理解这些最基础的动作抽象出来；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"让模型学会把一句自然语言拆解为一系列稳定、可回放的操作步骤；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"处理掉各种真实世界的“脏信息”：网络波动、弹窗打断、广告遮挡……\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"2024 年 10 月 25 日，我们发布了第一个能够在真机上稳定完成一条完整操作链路的 AutoGLM，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"它被业内视为全球首个具备 Phone Use 能力的 AI Agent。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"2.第一个由 AI 发出的红包\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h3\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"2024 年 11 月，AutoGLM 发出了人类历史上第一个由 AI 完成的手机红包：不是脚本录制，不是内嵌 API 调用，而是通过在屏幕上“看见”界面、“理解”含义，一步一步完成点击。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"对我们来说，这是一个信号：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"从此以后，手机上的很多交互，第一次可以完全由 AI 接手。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5a9e2b63f5a24437fc435\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":965,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:21:53.814Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:21:53.813Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/640.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"640.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":21164,\"width\":850,\"height\":566,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"3.走向云手机：把能力放到一个更安全的空间\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h3\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"2025 年\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，我们发布了 AutoGLM 2.0，验证了强化学习的规模扩展定律，提出了 MobileRL、ComputerRL 和 AgentRL 算法，让 AutoGLM 在上千个虚拟设备环境里同时强化学习，极大扩展了 Agent 的准确性和泛化能力。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"更关键的是，我们不希望 Agent 直接在用户真实手机、真实微信上肆意操作，于是选择把它放进一台和用户真实世界脱离的虚拟手机里：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"这台手机跑在云端；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"每一个动作都可以回放、审计、干预；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"真正敏感的数据可以严格隔离。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"这套设计背后的直觉很简单：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"让 AI 会用手机之前，我们要先保证，它不会在不该点的地方胡乱伸手。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"除了云手机的选择，我们主动放弃了操作微信等这些离用户隐私较近的 APP。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"为什么要开源？我们真正在意的是什么？\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"left\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"left\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"从产品的角度，AutoGLM 已经可以支撑起很多真实场景；从工程的角度，AutoGLM的积累足够写成一大摞技术报告。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"那为什么，在这个时间点，我们选择把它开源？\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们想清楚的，大概有三件事。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"1.这件事只在一家公司做，是不够的\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h3\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"AI 手机已经是趋势，但如果“会用手机的 AI 能力”只掌握在极少数厂商手里，那意味着：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"开发者的创新空间，要看平台愿不愿意开放接口；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"用户日常生活中最重要的那台设备，越来越像“别人家的入口”。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"AutoGLM 开源的第一层初衷，是把这一层能力变成整个行业可以共同拥有、共同打磨的公共底座。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"你可以把它当成一块积木，放进你自己的系统里，也可以把它拆开、重写、改造，那一刻起，它就不再只是“智谱的 AutoGLM”，而是你和你的团队做出来的东西的一部分。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"2.让隐私和控制权，真正留在使用方这一侧\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h3\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们也很清楚，Phone Use 能力，一旦做大，天然会碰到最敏感的那一部分世界：个人微信、支付、聊天记录、照片相册、企业内部系统。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们不希望也不应该，把这些东西握在自己手里。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"通过开源和私有化部署，企业和开发者可以在自己的合规环境中完整掌控数据、日志和权限。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"可以让手机，成为专属自己的 AI 手机。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"用一句话概括就是：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"技术向整个生态开放，数据与隐私，永远留在使用方这一侧。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"3.把我们走过的路，变成大家在Agent爆发时代的起跑线\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h3\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"AutoGLM是一条很陡的路：我们啃过的技术难题、踩过的坑、重写过的框架，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在很多场景里都可以复用，也值得被复用。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"但这还不够，“一花独放不是春”。Agent 的爆发，需要所有人一起参与。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们更乐见的是：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"有团队基于 AutoGLM，做出真正意义上的 AI 原生手机；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"有研究者把其中的某个模块拆出来，变成一篇论文、一套新算法；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"有个人开发者把一个 Demo 改成自己的项目，在某个小众场景里真正跑起来。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们希望开源社区：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"从今天开始，人人都可以拥有自己的手机 Agent。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"你现在能拿到什么\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"left\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"left\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们开源的，是一整套可以「拿来就用」的能力，而不仅仅是一份概念说明。具体包括：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"训练好的核心模型；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Phone Use 能力框架与工具链；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"可直接跑通的 Demo，覆盖 50+ 高频中文 App；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"针对 Android 的适配层与示例工程；\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"文档、快速上手指南。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"模型会以 MIT 开源许可证的形式开放，而所有代码会以 Apache-2.0 开源许可证的形式，托管在 GitHub 仓库（示例：github.com/zai-org/Open-AutoGLM）中。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"你可以把它当成一套现成的基础设施，也可以单独拆用其中的某一部分，甚至可以把它改得面目全非——只要它帮助你更接近你心目中的「AI 原生手机」。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"接下来\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"left\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"现在的 AutoGLM 不是一个完美的答案。真实世界的手机和应用，它还远远没有全部见过。未来的 AI 手机生态，也一定会有比我们今天想象得更惊喜的形态。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们做的，只是把对“AI 会不会用手机”这个问题的一次完整回答，诚实地、原原本本地，交到你们手里。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在 2025 年尾的这个时刻，正如 Andrej Karpathy 所说，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"从今天开始，人人都可以拥有自己的手机 Agent。我们面对的大概不只是“Agent 元年”，而更可能是“Agent 的十年”。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"接下来，AutoGLM 团队会继续努力，让我们一起推动 Agent 开源和研究，那个梦想中的“贾维斯”，才会真的在我们人人身边出现。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"root\",\"version\":1}},\"contentType_en\":\"external\",\"externalUrl_en\":\"https://autoglm.z.ai/blog/\",\"content_en\":null,\"featured\":false,\"thumbnail_zh\":null,\"thumbnail_en\":null,\"active\":true,\"order\":0,\"tag_zh\":[\"Agent\"],\"tag_en\":[\"Agentic LLM\"],\"apiConfig_zh\":null,\"apiConfig_en\":null,\"experienceUrl_zh\":null,\"experienceUrl_en\":null,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-21T04:30:38.572Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-01-07T02:51:10.889Z\"},\"title_zh\":\"AutoGLM\",\"title_en\":\"AutoGLM\",\"desc_zh\":\"自主规划并执行复杂多步骤任务的智能体模型\",\"desc_en\":\"An intelligent agent model that autonomously plans and executes complex, multi-step tasks\",\"showNew\":false,\"active\":true,\"order\":5,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T03:58:31.136Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-19T12:49:50.867Z\"}],\"children\":\"$L15\"}]}]}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"12:[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"isMobile\":false,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L14\",null,{\"navConfig\":[{\"id\":4,\"article\":{\"id\":156,\"title_zh\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo发布：多模态Coding基座模型\",\"title_en\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo: A Multimodal Coding Foundation Model\",\"createAt\":\"2026-04-01T16:00:00.000Z\",\"category\":\"blog\",\"resume_zh\":null,\"resume_en\":\"A multimodal coding foundation model for visual programming\",\"contentType_zh\":\"content\",\"externalUrl_zh\":null,\"content_zh\":{\"root\":{\"children\":[{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Agent时代，模型能力由模型智能以及其处理的context容量两个维度定义。一个能够原生处理图片、视频、文本等多模态context，同时擅长复杂编程、长程规划、动作执行的Coding基座模型，将是所有AI原生应用的基石。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"今天，我们发布\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，面向视觉编程打造的多模态Coding基座模型。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo从预训练阶段深度融合视觉与文本能力，让编程不再局限于纯文本输入。模型能看懂设计稿、截图、网页界面，并据此生成完整可运行的代码，真正做到看得懂画面、写得出代码。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf9751f21c2c2005c82ca7\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":955,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:32:49.527Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:32:49.526Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/%E6%99%BA%E8%B0%B1-%E4%B8%BBCase-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-0402%20(1).m4v\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"智谱-主Case-中文-0402 (1).m4v\",\"mimeType\":\"video/mp4\",\"filesize\":159012884,\"width\":null,\"height\":null,\"focalX\":null,\"focalY\":null}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"核心要点如下：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"原生多模态Coding基座：原生理解图片、视频、设计稿、文档版面等多模态输入，并支持画框、截图、读网页等多模态工具调用，上下文窗口扩展至200k，将Agent的感知-行动链路从纯文本延伸到视觉交互。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"兼顾视觉与编程能力：在多模态Coding、Tool Use、GUI Agent等核心基准上取得领先表现。通过多任务协同RL等技术手段，确保纯文本场景下的编程、推理、工具调用等能力不退化。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"深度适配Claude Code与龙虾场景：与Claude Code、OpenClaw/AutoClaw等Agent深度协同，支持“看懂环境→规划动作→执行任务”的完整闭环，并提供全套官方Skills，开箱即用。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"多模态Coding基座\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h1\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在多模态Coding、Agentic任务以及纯文本Coding维度的评测基准上，GLM-5V-Turbo均以更小尺寸取得了领先表现。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf9774f21c2c2005c82ca8\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":956,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:33:24.383Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:33:24.382Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/download_image.png\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"download_image.png\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\",\"filesize\":165654,\"width\":1080,\"height\":747,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo在设计稿还原、视觉代码生成、多模态检索与问答、视觉探查等基准上均取得领先表现；在衡量真实GUI环境操控能力的AndroidWorld、WebVoyager等基准上同样表现突出。在纯文本Coding能力方面，GLM-5V-Turbo在CC-Bench-V2的Backend、Frontend和Repo Exploration三项核心基准测试中均保持稳定表现，表明\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"视觉能力引入后，纯文本编程与推理能力保持了同等水准\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf9787f21c2c2005c82ca9\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":957,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:33:43.131Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:33:43.130Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/download_image%20(1).png\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"download_image (1).png\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\",\"filesize\":100903,\"width\":1080,\"height\":381,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在AutoClaw等龙虾Agent中接入GLM-5V-Turbo后，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"龙虾具备了真正的视觉能力，能看懂屏幕上的信息\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。模型在衡量龙虾Agent任务执行质量的PinchBench、ClawEval和ZClawBench上取得优异成绩，验证了其在复杂任务执行场景中的综合能力。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"内测阶段，字节跳动、美团、快手等互联网大厂\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"合作伙伴对GLM-5V-Turbo给予了高度评价\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"“GLM-5V-Turbo实现了从设计稿到代码的完整还原，作为一款视觉理解模型，能够很好地满足开发者的前端开发场景。”——TRAE模型测评团队\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"quote\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"“原生多模态能力的引入并未削弱其编程逻辑，其编程能力仍属于国内第一梯队。增强了AI at Work领域下D2C、图片处理等方向的工作体验。”——美团某团队\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"quote\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"“它为Agent安上了「眼睛」，同时在编程领域展现出优于同类多模态模型的能力，在视觉编程场景中更具竞争力。”——快手万擎模型测评团队\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"quote\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo能够取得性能领先在于其\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"模型架构、训练方法、数据构造、工具链四个层面的系统性升级\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"原生多模态融合：GLM-5V-Turbo从预训练阶段开始进行文本与视觉能力深度融合，并在后训练阶段实现多模态协同优化。我们研发了新一代CogViT视觉编码器，在通用物体识别、细粒度理解、几何与空间感知上均达最优，也设计了兼容多模态输入且推理友好的MTP结构，在多模态场景下实现了较高的推理效率。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"30+ 任务协同强化学习：在强化学习阶段同时优化30+任务类型，覆盖STEM、grounding、video、GUI Agent等子领域，模型在感知、推理、Agentic执行和人类体感上均获稳健提升，协同强化学习有效缓解了单领域训练的不稳定性。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Agentic数据与任务构造：针对Agent数据稀缺和验证困难的行业挑战，我们构建从元素感知到序列级动作预测的多层级体系，基于合成环境大规模生成可控、可验证的训练数据，并从预训练阶段即注入Agentic元能力（如将GUI Agent PRM数据加入预训练以降低幻觉），同时探索非对称优化，用多模态评估任务撬动更强的Agent能力。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"多模态工具链扩展：在文本工具基础上，GLM-5V-Turbo新增支持多模态搜索、画框、截图、读网页等多模态tools，将编程与任务执行的感知-行动链路从纯文本扩展到视觉交互。与Claude Code、AutoClaw等龙虾的协同效果进一步增强，支持“看懂环境→规划动作→执行任务”的完整闭环。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"典型场景展示\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h1\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"1.图像即代码\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo尤其擅长核心视觉编程场景。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf97b8f21c2c2005c82caa\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":958,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:34:32.555Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:34:32.554Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/%E6%99%BA%E8%B0%B1-%E9%A2%9D%E5%A4%96Case1-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-0402%20(1).m4v\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"智谱-额外Case1-中文-0402 (1).m4v\",\"mimeType\":\"video/mp4\",\"filesize\":40523666,\"width\":null,\"height\":null,\"focalX\":null,\"focalY\":null}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"前端复刻\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：发送草图、设计稿、参考网站的截图或录屏，模型就能直接理解布局、配色、组件层级与交互逻辑，生成完整可运行的前端工程，准确还原版式、配色、动效等视觉细节。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GUI自主探索复刻\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：结合Claude Code等框架，GLM-5V-Turbo能凭借自身强大的GUI Agent能力自主探索目标网站，浏览页面结构、梳理各页面之间的跳转关系、采集视觉素材与交互细节，最后基于记录的探索结果直接生成代码复现整个站点，实现从“看图复刻”到“GUI探索复刻”的能力跃升。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"交互式编辑\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：支持按需求增删页面模块、修改文案与样式、调整布局结构，并可补充按钮反馈、弹窗切换、表单联动等交互功能，实现可视化迭代编辑。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"2.为龙虾安上眼睛\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"龙虾的任务边界被大幅拓宽\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，例如可以浏览网页和文档，生成图文并茂的报告、PPT，还可以查询并解读K线图等复杂图表。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"AutoClaw已上线“股票分析师”Skill，利用GLM-5V-Turbo的原生视觉能力，龙虾能直接看懂K线走势、估值区间图和券商研报图表，实现四路数据源60秒并行采集，输出\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"图文交错\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"的研报。立即在AutoClaw中\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"切换至GLM-5V-Turbo\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，试试提问“帮我分析今天XXX的股价，生成专业分析报告”。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"除视觉编程与龙虾任务外，GLM-5V-Turbo在多模态搜索、深度研究、GUI Agent、感知Grounding等更广泛的Agentic场景中也实现了显著的性能提升。为此，我们提供了一组\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"官方Skills\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，涵盖图像Captioning、视觉Grounding、基于文档的写作、简历筛选、提示词生成等原生能力，以及基于GLM-OCR和GLM-Image构建的文字识别、表格识别、手写体识别、公式识别和文生图能力，帮助用户在更多场景中释放模型的多模态潜力。上述Skills已上线ClawHub，一键安装即可体验全部能力。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"ClawHub链接\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"https://clawhub.ai/zai-org/glm-master-skill\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"link\",\"version\":3,\"fields\":{\"url\":\"https://clawhub.ai/zai-org/glm-master-skill\",\"newTab\":true,\"linkType\":\"custom\"},\"id\":\"69d8a70049068ea474ee78c4\"}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GitHub链接：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-skills\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"link\",\"version\":3,\"fields\":{\"url\":\"https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-skills\",\"newTab\":true,\"linkType\":\"custom\"},\"id\":\"69d8a75849068ea474ee78c5\"}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"立即体验\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h1\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"欢迎广大用户通过以下方式接入GLM-5V-Turbo：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"1.产品体验\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h3\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"AutoClaw（澳龙）：https://autoglm.zhipuai.cn/autoclaw/\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Z.ai：https://chat.z.ai\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"2.官方API接入\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h3\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"BigModel\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\" 开放平台\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/vlm/glm-5v-turbo\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Z.ai：https://docs.z.ai/guides/vlm/glm-5v-turbo\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Coding Plan：现面向Coding Plan用户开放申请；后续GLM Coding Plan也会纳入GLM-5V-Turbo，敬请期待。申请问卷：https://zhipu-ai.feishu.cn/share/base/form/shrcndgpmRlJoD5rMmIavUrPwzg\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf9827f21c2c2005c82cab\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":959,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:36:23.345Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:36:23.344Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/da5d94bc5f15e2975fc6f4b5468036c8.png\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"da5d94bc5f15e2975fc6f4b5468036c8.png\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\",\"filesize\":588642,\"width\":1170,\"height\":1449,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"root\",\"version\":1}},\"contentType_en\":\"content\",\"externalUrl_en\":null,\"content_en\":null,\"featured\":false,\"thumbnail_zh\":null,\"thumbnail_en\":null,\"active\":true,\"order\":0,\"tag_zh\":[\"基座模型\"],\"tag_en\":[\"Mutimodal AI\"],\"apiConfig_zh\":null,\"apiConfig_en\":null,\"experienceUrl_zh\":null,\"experienceUrl_en\":null,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-21T04:52:36.490Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:36:51.645Z\"},\"title_zh\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo\",\"title_en\":\"GLM-5V-Turbo\",\"desc_zh\":\"面向视觉编程打造的多模态Coding基座模型\",\"desc_en\":\"Multimodal Coding Model\",\"showNew\":true,\"active\":true,\"order\":1,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T03:51:02.522Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-19T12:48:26.455Z\"},{\"id\":1,\"article\":{\"id\":155,\"title_zh\":\"GLM-5-Turbo：龙虾增强的基座模型\",\"title_en\":\"GLM-5-Turbo: A Foundation Model Enhanced for OpenClaw\",\"createAt\":\"2026-03-15T16:00:00.000Z\",\"category\":\"blog\",\"resume_zh\":null,\"resume_en\":\"A foundation model for OpenClaw\",\"contentType_zh\":\"content\",\"externalUrl_zh\":null,\"content_zh\":{\"root\":{\"children\":[{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们推出GLM-5-Turbo——一个面向OpenClaw龙虾场景深度优化的基座模型。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"体验过OpenClaw的用户都有一个共同感受：模型能聊好天，但未必能干好活。问题的根源不在框架，而在底层模型本身。通用大模型在进入真实复杂的Agent场景后，容易在长链路任务中失速。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Harness再多，不如模型自身变强。GLM-5-Turbo从训练阶段就针对龙虾任务的核心需求进行专项优化，增强如工具调用、指令遵循、定时与持续性任务、长链路执行等核心能力。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在自研基准测试ZClawBench中取得国产模型第一的成绩\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"；多家互联网大厂在龙虾场景内测中给予高度评价。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们推出\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Claw龙虾套餐\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，及面向企业级场景的Claw安全管理体系。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"龙虾原生模型\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"tag\":\"h1\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"龙虾任务不是简单的一问一答，通常涉及多轮理解、任务拆解、工具调用、状态衔接、时间触发和持续执行的长链路工作流。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"通用模型\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"即使在对话能力上表现优秀，一旦进入真实龙虾场景，仍然容易出现指令遵循偏差、工具调用不稳定、长任务中途失速等问题。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"要从根本上解决这些难题，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"必须在基座模型层进行深度优化\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"——这正是GLM-5-Turbo的出发点。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"从训练数据构造到优化目标设计，我们构造真实Agent工作流使模型在龙虾任务中具备可执行性。重点增强以下核心能力：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Tool Calling——调用不掉链子。强化对外部工具与各类Skills的调用能力。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Instruction Following——复杂指令拆解更强。对复杂多层、长链路指令理解和拆解更准确，支持识别目标、规划步骤、多智能体协同。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"定时与持续性任务——更懂时间维度，长任务不中断。针对定时触发、长时间运行等场景进行重点优化，能够更好理解时间维度上的要求。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"高吞吐长链路——执行更稳。针对数据吞吐量大、链条长的任务进一步提升执行效率与稳定性，适合长程业务流程。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"type\":\"linebreak\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"龙虾场景基准ZClawBench\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"tag\":\"h1\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"随着龙虾OpenClaw的普及，如何评测模型在龙虾场景的能力成为全行业焦点。基于对OpenClaw大量真实用例的分析，我们发布龙虾场景端到端Agent评测基准ZClawBench。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"当前OpenClaw的任务类型覆盖安装配置、代码开发、信息搜集、数据分析、内容创作等多元化任务，用户群体也从早期的开发者扩展到效率办公人群、金融从业者、运维工程师、内容创作者与研究分析人员等。同时，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Skills的使用比例在短时间内从26%快速增长至45%\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，表明Agent能力正向模块化与技能化的生态方向演进。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"基于该基准的评测结果显示，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5-Turbo在OpenClaw场景中的表现相比GLM-5提升显著，在多项关键任务上整体领先于多家主流模型。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf95dff21c2c2005c82c9d\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":951,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:26:39.011Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:26:39.009Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/111.png\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"111.png\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\",\"filesize\":1194870,\"width\":3255,\"height\":2270,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"ZClawBench的题库与测试轨迹已全面公开，欢迎业界共同验证与完善。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"用户真实体验是试金石。GLM-5-Turbo以Pony-Alpha-2为代号接入AutoClaw澳龙，在用户盲测中，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"90%\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"的受访者认为GLM-5-Turbo的表现优于其他国产模型。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"内测阶段，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"龙虾生态的互联网大厂对GLM-5-Turbo给予高度评价\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"“精准的工具调用配合长程任务的稳定可靠，完美驱动了桌面级Agent上的跨应用数据流转与系统API操控。在攻克办公场景的‘幻觉’痛点上表现优秀！”——阿里QoderWork模型测评团队\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"quote\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"“指令遵循力压群雄，面对长任务更精准不掉链子，极大提升了多智能体构建的成功率。”——扣子Coze测评团队\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"quote\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"“定时与长链路任务稳健，对比同类模型展现出明显第一梯队的优势，非常靠谱。”——美团某团队\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"quote\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"“高吞吐执行极快且不失速，响应稳定性领跑同类模型，真正解决了Agent的执行难题。”——快手万擎测评团队\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"quote\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在编程场景，GLM-5-Turbo延续GLM模型\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Agentic Engineering\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"的表现：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"“编程能力稳居第一梯队，在Coding Agent实测中优于同类模型，处理长链路代码任务非常稳健。”——字节TRAE团队\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"quote\",\"version\":1},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5-Turbo已接入软通动力旗下机械革命盒子中，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"面向全球首发接入GLM模型的机械革命“龙虾盒子”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，打造原生AI Agent终端体验。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf95f3f21c2c2005c82c9e\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":952,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:26:59.699Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:26:59.698Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/222.png\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"222.png\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\",\"filesize\":1412232,\"width\":1932,\"height\":810,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"龙虾套餐喂饱你的AI同事\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"tag\":\"h1\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"龙虾太能干活，自然也吃tokens。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"一个典型的龙虾任务，比如完成一次跨部门的会议纪要整理与任务分发，可能涉及数十轮工具调用与上下文衔接，tokens消耗远超普通对话。对于使用龙虾的企业和个人来说，tokens成为最大的成本瓶颈。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"为了让企业和个人实现龙虾“tokens自由”，智谱即日起推出基于GLM-5-Turbo的龙虾套餐，包含个人版和Team版。无论你是一人公司、创业团队，或者是大中型企业，都能根据自身业务规模灵活订阅套餐。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf9609f21c2c2005c82c9f\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":953,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:27:21.208Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:27:21.208Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/333-2.png\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"333-2.png\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\",\"filesize\":312315,\"width\":1280,\"height\":604,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"每个账号最多购买5个。企业可通过龙虾套餐Team版，按照实际员工数灵活订阅，以可控成本实现tokens的充分保障以及AI员工的稳定在线。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"此外，我们在龙虾套餐的基础上，专门构建了\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"一套面向企业级场景的OpenClaw安全管理体系“Claw for Enterprise Security”\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。支持对不同类型Claw的统一调度与权限编排——无论是信息搜集、数据分析、代码开发还是跨系统操作，企业可以根据业务流程灵活组合Claw能力，并通过集中化的管控台对每一个Agent任务的执行路径、工具调用链路和资源消耗进行实时可视化监控，让复杂的多Agent协同不再是黑盒。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在安全保障层面，该系统提供多层防护机制\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"：基于角色的权限管理确保每个Claw只能在授权范围内调用工具和访问数据；所有操作均生成完整的审计日志，满足企业合规要求；敏感业务数据全程加密处理，严格遵守数据本地化要求，不离开企业可控边界；关键业务节点保留人工审批机制，防止自动化流程产生不可控的业务风险。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"正在到来的变革是，以OpenClaw为代表的Agent正在进入组织内部，让每一家企业都拥有7×24小时在线、随叫随到的AI员工；同时，它们也成为我们每个人的专属AI助理，把人从流程化、重复性的琐事中真正解放出来。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们正在见证大模型从提效工具，走向企业劳动力的一场关键跃迁。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"接入与使用\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"tag\":\"h1\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5-Turbo现已上线，开发者和企业用户可以通过智谱开放平台\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"BigModel.cn\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"直接调用API，或者通过龙虾套餐接入。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM Coding Plan Max现已支持GLM-5-Turbo，Pro套餐将在本月尽快支持，Lite套餐将在4月支持接入。Coding Plan也可用于OpenClaw接入体验；如需长期稳定运行、后台持续执行或更高负载的Agent场景，建议优先使用龙虾套餐。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5、GLM-5-Turbo作为对标Claude Opus的高阶模型，将按照“高峰期3倍，非高峰期2倍”系数消耗额度。作为限时福利，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-5-Turbo将在非高峰期仅作1倍抵扣持续到4月底。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"AutoClaw澳龙默认模型为GLM-5-Turbo，让所有非程序员群体可以体验GLM-5-Turbo龙虾能力，享受一定免费额度。即日起至3月22日为澳龙限时福利，加油包最高享3.4折优惠（加油包自购买起7日内有效）。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69cf964af21c2c2005c82ca0\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":954,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:28:26.424Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:28:26.423Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/444.png\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"444.png\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\",\"filesize\":63251,\"width\":1706,\"height\":540,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"官方 API 接入\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"智谱开放平台：BigModel.cn\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Z.ai：api.z.ai\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM Coding Plan\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Coding Plan Max已纳入GLM-5-Turbo\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Pro版将在本月尽快支持\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在线体验\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"AutoClaw澳龙客户端：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"https://autoglm.zhipuai.cn/autoclaw\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Z.ai：z.ai\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"智谱清言APP/网页版\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"start\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"root\",\"version\":1}},\"contentType_en\":\"content\",\"externalUrl_en\":null,\"content_en\":null,\"featured\":true,\"thumbnail_zh\":null,\"thumbnail_en\":null,\"active\":true,\"order\":0,\"tag_zh\":[\"基座模型\",\"Agent\"],\"tag_en\":[\"Agentic LLM\"],\"apiConfig_zh\":null,\"apiConfig_en\":null,\"experienceUrl_zh\":null,\"experienceUrl_en\":null,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-21T04:54:19.553Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-03T10:29:20.932Z\"},\"title_zh\":\"GLM-5-Turbo\",\"title_en\":\"GLM-5-Turbo\",\"desc_zh\":\"专为龙虾场景打造的基座模型\",\"desc_en\":\"Built for Claw\",\"showNew\":true,\"active\":true,\"order\":2,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T03:55:54.590Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-19T12:45:35.934Z\"},{\"id\":3,\"article\":{\"id\":158,\"title_zh\":\"智谱联合华为开源首个国产芯片训练的多模态SOTA模型\",\"title_en\":\"GLM-Image: Auto-regressive for  Dense-knowledge and High-fidelity  Image Generation\",\"createAt\":\"2026-01-13T16:00:00.000Z\",\"category\":\"blog\",\"resume_zh\":null,\"resume_en\":\"the first open-source, industrial-grade discrete auto-regressive image generation model\",\"contentType_zh\":\"content\",\"externalUrl_zh\":null,\"content_zh\":{\"root\":{\"children\":[{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"今天，智谱联合华为开源新一代图像生成模型\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-Image\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，模型基于昇腾Atlas 800T A2设备和昇思MindSpore AI框架完成从数据到训练的全流程，是\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"首个在国产芯片上完成全程训练的SOTA多模态模型\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-Image采用自主创新的「自回归+扩散解码器」混合架构，实现了图像生成与语言模型的联合，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"是我们面向以Nano Banana Pro为代表的新一代「认知型生成」技术范式的一次重要探索\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"核心亮点如下：\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"架构革新，面向「认知型生成」的技术探索：采用创新的「自回归 + 扩散编码器」混合架构，兼顾全局指令理解与局部细节刻画，克服了海报、PPT、科普图等知识密集型场景生成难题，向探索以Nano Banana Pro为代表的新一代“知识+推理”的认知型生成模型迈出了重要一步。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"listitem\",\"version\":1,\"value\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"首个在国产芯片完成全程训练的SOTA模型：模型自回归结构基座基于昇腾Atlas 800T A2设备与昇思MindSpore AI框架，完成了从数据预处理到大规模训练的全流程构建，验证了在国产全栈算力底座上训练前沿模型的可行性。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"listitem\",\"version\":1,\"value\":2},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"文字渲染开源SOTA：在CVTG-2K（复杂视觉文本生成）和LongText-Bench（长文本渲染）榜单获得开源第一，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"尤其擅长汉字生成任务\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"listitem\",\"version\":1,\"value\":3},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"高性价比与速度优化：API调用模式下，生成一张图片\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"仅需0.1元\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"，速度优化版本即将更新。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"listitem\",\"version\":1,\"value\":4}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"list\",\"version\":1,\"listType\":\"bullet\",\"start\":1,\"tag\":\"ul\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"架构创新：读懂指令，写对文字\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"近期，以\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"Nano Banana Pro\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"为代表的闭源图像生成模型正在推动图像生成与大语言模型的深度融合。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"技术范式正从单一的图像生成，进化为兼具世界知识与推理能力的「认知型生成」\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。这些模型在海报、PPT、科普图等知识密集型场景及高保真细节呈现上表现惊艳，展现了这一技术范式的优势。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-Image正是我们面向「认知型生成」技术范式一次重要探索。这是首个开源的工业表现级离散自回归图像生成模型，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"我们希望借此与开源社区分享我们在这一前沿方向的技术路径与实践思考\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"创新架构让模型读懂写对：面对传统模型在“理解复杂指令”与“精准绘制文字”上难以兼顾的问题，GLM-Image 引入了「自回归+扩散解码器」混合架构，创新地融合了9B大小的自回归模型与7B大小的DiT扩散解码器。前者利用其语言模型的底座优势，专注于提升对指令的语义理解和画面的全局构图；后者配合Glyph Encoder的文本编码器，专注于还原图像的高频细节和文字笔画，以此改善模型“提笔忘字”的现象。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"listitem\",\"version\":1,\"value\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"多分辨率自适应：通过改进Tokenizer策略，GLM-Image能够自适应处理多种分辨率，原生支持从1024x1024到2048×2048尺寸的任意比例图像的生成任务，无需重新训练。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"listitem\",\"version\":1,\"value\":2}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"list\",\"version\":1,\"listType\":\"bullet\",\"start\":1,\"tag\":\"ul\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5af6adca8453370f68fbb\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":966,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:28:44.916Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:28:44.915Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/1-2.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"1-2.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":20036,\"width\":1080,\"height\":265,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":2,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"通用pipeline\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":2,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5af7cdca8453370f68fbc\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":967,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:28:59.459Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:28:59.459Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/2-2.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"2-2.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":24028,\"width\":1080,\"height\":411,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":2,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"解码器结构示意图\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":2,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"开源SOTA：更擅长文字密集生成任务\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"基于上述架构创新，GLM-Image在文字渲染的权威榜单中达到开源SOTA水平。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5af94dca8453370f68fbd\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":968,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:35:49.320Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:35:49.319Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/3-2.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"3-2.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":25520,\"width\":1080,\"height\":436,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"CVTG-2K（复杂视觉文字生成）\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"榜单核心考察模型在图像中同时生成多处文字的准确性。在多区域文字生成准确率上，GLM-Image凭借0.9116的Word Accuracy（文字准确率）成绩，位列开源模型第一。在NED（归一化编辑距离）指标上，GLM-Image同样以0.9557领先，表明其生成的文字与目标文字高度一致，错字、漏字情况更少。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"listitem\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":1,\"value\":1},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"LongText-Bench（长文本渲染）榜单考察模型渲染长文本、多行文字的准确性，覆盖招牌、海报、PPT、对话框等8种文字密集场景，并分设中英双语测试，GLM-Image以英文0.952、中文0.979的成绩位列开源模型第一。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"listitem\",\"version\":1,\"value\":2}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"list\",\"version\":1,\"listType\":\"bullet\",\"start\":1,\"tag\":\"ul\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"首个国产芯片训练出的SOTA模型\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-Image是我们对国产计算生态的一次深度探索与验证。其自回归结构基座从早期的数据预处理到最终的大规模预训练，全流程均在昇腾Atlas 800T A2设备上完成。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"依托昇腾NPU和昇思MindSpore AI框架，使用动态图多级流水下发、高性能融合算子、多流并行等特性，我们自研了模型训练套件，全面优化数据预处理、预训练、SFT和RL的端到端流程。通过动态图的多级流水优化机制，将Host侧算子下发的关键阶段流水化并高度重叠，消除下发瓶颈；通过多流并行策略，通信和计算互掩，打破文本梯度同步、图像特征广播等操作的通信墙，极致优化性能；使用AdamW EMA、COC、RMS Norm等昇腾亲和的高性能融合算子，同步提升训练的稳定性和性能。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-Image是首个在国产芯片上完成全流程训练的SOTA多模态模型，\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":1,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"验证了在国产全栈算力底座上训练高性能多模态生成模型的可行性\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1},{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"。我们希望这一实践能为社区挖掘国产算力潜力提供有价值的参考。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5afafdca8453370f68fbe\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":969,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:36:23.915Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:36:23.915Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/4-2.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"4-2.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":40456,\"width\":1080,\"height\":471,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"实测案例\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"heading\",\"version\":1,\"tag\":\"h2\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"让我们来看看GLM-Image在实际的复杂图文任务中的表现。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"场景一：科普插画\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-Image 更擅长绘制包含复杂逻辑流程与文字说明的科普插画及原理示意图。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5afc2dca8453370f68fbf\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":970,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:37:01.387Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:37:01.386Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/5-2.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"5-2.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":97304,\"width\":1080,\"height\":684,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5afcadca8453370f68fc0\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":971,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:37:15.244Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:37:15.243Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/6-1.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"6-1.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":107422,\"width\":1080,\"height\":684,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"场景二：多格图画\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"在生成电商图、漫画等多格图画时，GLM-Image能够保持风格和主体的一致性，并保障多处文字生成的准确率。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5afd7dca8453370f68fc1\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":972,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:37:37.777Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:37:37.776Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/7-1.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"7-1.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":91728,\"width\":1080,\"height\":616,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"场景三：社交媒体图文封面\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[{\"detail\":0,\"format\":0,\"mode\":\"normal\",\"style\":\"\",\"text\":\"GLM-Image 适用于制作社交媒体封面及内容等排版复杂的图片，让您的创作更自由丰富。\",\"type\":\"text\",\"version\":1}],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\":0,\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"version\":1,\"textFormat\":0,\"textStyle\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"upload\",\"version\":3,\"format\":\"\",\"id\":\"69e5afe5dca8453370f68fc2\",\"fields\":null,\"relationTo\":\"media\",\"value\":{\"id\":973,\"alt\":\" \",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:38:02.547Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-20T04:38:02.546Z\",\"url\":\"/api/media/file/8-1.webp\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"8-1.webp\",\"mimeType\":\"image/webp\",\"filesize\":135654,\"width\":1080,\"height\":1461,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50}},{\"children\":[],\"direction\":null,\"format\":\"justify\",\"indent\